{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875778427,"sessionID":"ses_2858e4900ffeHni7jjmb7lEFcK","part":{"id":"prt_d7a71e540001Hwm4girv3HMEo2","messageID":"msg_d7a71dad6001R2zxk8kpCXJooX","sessionID":"ses_2858e4900ffeHni7jjmb7lEFcK","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-dc0d5b4ea02d4acd82b17dbd3aacb45d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cmd/cli/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cmd/cli/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # CLI Build Command Design\n2: \n3: **AR**: AR-021 — CLI build 命令  \n4: **Module**: cmd/cli  \n5: **Language**: Python  \n6: **Size**: M\n7: \n8: ## Overview\n9: \n10: The `build` command is a core component of the AgentCube CLI that builds container images from packaged agent workspaces. It supports both local Docker builds and cloud-based builds, with automatic version management and comprehensive error handling.\n11: \n12: ## Architecture\n13: \n14: ### Component Diagram\n15: \n16: ```\n17: ┌─────────────┐\n18: │   CLI (Typer)   │\n19: │  main.py     │\n20: └──────┬──────┘\n21:        │ build()\n22:        ▼\n23: ┌─────────────────────┐\n24: │  BuildRuntime       │\n25: │  build_runtime.py   │\n26: └──────┬──────────────┘\n27:        │\n28:        ├──► MetadataService\n29:        │    └── load_metadata()\n30:        │    └── save_metadata()\n31:        │\n32:        └──► DockerService\n33:             └── check_docker_available()\n34:             └── build_image()\n35:             └── get_image_info()\n36: ```\n37: \n38: ### Key Components\n39: \n40: 1. **CLI Layer** (`agentcube/cli/main.py`)\n41:    - Typer command definition\n42:    - User input validation\n43:    - Error handling and user feedback\n44: \n45: 2. **Runtime Layer** (`agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`)\n46:    - Build orchestration\n47:    - Version management\n48:    - Build mode selection\n49: \n50: 3. **Service Layer**\n51:    - `MetadataService`: Metadata persistence and loading\n52:    - `DockerService`: Docker operations (build, push, etc.)\n53: \n54: ## Data Structures\n55: \n56: ### BuildOptions\n57: \n58: Dictionary containing build command options:\n59: \n60: ```python\n61: {\n62:     \"proxy\": Optional[str],          # Proxy URL for dependency resolution\n63:     \"cloud_provider\": Optional[str], # Cloud provider name (e.g., \"huawei\")\n64:     \"output\": Optional[str],         # Output path for build artifacts\n65: }\n66: ```\n67: \n68: ### BuildResult\n69: \n70: Dictionary containing build output information:\n71: \n72: ```python\n73: {\n74:     \"image_name\": str,       # Full image name with tag (e.g., \"agent:1.0.0\")\n75:     \"image_id\": str,         # Docker image ID (short form, 12 chars)\n76:     \"image_size\": str,       # Human-readable size (e.g., \"512.34 MB\")\n77:     \"size_bytes\": int,       # Size in bytes\n78:     \"build_time\": float,     # Unix timestamp of build completion\n79: }\n80: ```\n81: \n82: ### AgentMetadata Fields (Build-related)\n83: \n84: Relevant fields from `AgentMetadata` for build operations:\n85: \n86: ```python\n87: agent_name: str              # Used as image name\n88: version: Optional[str]       # Semantic version (auto-incremented)\n89: build_mode: str              # \"local\" or \"cloud\"\n90: image: Optional[Dict[str, Any]]  # Build result storage\n91: ```\n92: \n93: ## API Contracts\n94: \n95: ### BuildRuntime.build()\n96: \n97: ```python\n98: def build(\n99:     self,\n100:     workspace_path: Path,\n101:     **options: Any\n102: ) -> Dict[str, Any]\n103: ```\n104: \n105: **Purpose**: Build a container image from a packaged agent workspace.\n106: \n107: **Parameters**:\n108: - `workspace_path` (Path): Path to the agent workspace directory\n109: - `options` (Dict[str, Any]): Build options including proxy, cloud_provider, output\n110: \n111: **Returns**: `BuildResult` dictionary\n112: \n113: **Behavior**:\n114: 1. Loads metadata from workspace\n115: 2. Validates build prerequisites (Dockerfile exists, Docker available)\n116: 3. Increments version (with rollback on failure)\n117: 4. Executes build based on `build_mode` in metadata\n118: 5. Updates metadata with build results\n119: 6. Returns build result\n120: \n121: **Raises**:\n122: - `ValueError`: If Dockerfile not found or prerequisites not met\n123: - `RuntimeError`: If Docker is not available or build fails\n124: - `FileNotFoundError`: If metadata file not found\n125: \n126: ### BuildRuntime._build_local()\n127: \n128: ```python\n129: def _build_local(\n130:     self,\n131:     workspace_path: Path,\n132:     metadata: AgentMetadata,\n133:     options: Dict[str, Any]\n134: ) -> Dict[str, Any]\n135: ```\n136: \n137: **Purpose**: Build image using local Docker daemon.\n138: \n139: **Parameters**:\n140: - `workspace_path` (Path): Path to workspace (used as build context)\n141: - `metadata` (AgentMetadata): Agent metadata containing name and version\n142: - `options` (Dict[str, Any]): Build options (proxy support)\n143: \n144: **Behavior**:\n145: - Constructs image name from `agent_name` and `version`\n146: - Optionally adds proxy build arguments if proxy provided\n147: - Delegates to `DockerService.build_image()`\n148: - Adds image name to result\n149: \n150: ### BuildRuntime._build_cloud()\n151: \n152: ```python\n153: def _build_cloud(\n154:     self,\n155:     workspace_path: Path,\n156:     metadata: AgentMetadata,\n157:     options: Dict[str, Any]\n158: ) -> Dict[str, Any]\n159: ```\n160: \n161: **Purpose**: Build image in cloud provider (placeholder implementation).\n162: \n163: **Parameters**:\n164: - `workspace_path` (Path): Path to workspace\n165: - `metadata` (AgentMetadata): Agent metadata\n166: - `options` (Dict[str, Any]): Build options including cloud_provider\n167: \n168: **Behavior**:\n169: - Returns placeholder build result with cloud provider prefix\n170: - Logs cloud provider name\n171: \n172: ### BuildRuntime._increment_version()\n173: \n174: ```python\n175: def _increment_version(\n176:     self,\n177:     workspace_path: Path,\n178:     metadata: AgentMetadata\n179: ) -> str\n180: ```\n181: \n182: **Purpose**: Increment agent version before build.\n183: \n184: **Parameters**:\n185: - `workspace_path` (Path): Path to workspace (for saving metadata)\n186: - `metadata` (AgentMetadata): Agent metadata to modify\n187: \n188: **Returns**: New version string\n189: \n190: **Version Rules**:\n191: 1. **Semantic version** (X.Y.Z): Increment patch (Z)\n192: 2. **Semantic version with prerelease** (X.Y.Z-N.suffix): Increment prerelease number (N)\n193: 3. **Non-semantic version**: Append \".1\"\n194: 4. **No version**: Set to \"0.1.0\"\n195: \n196: **Examples**:\n197: - `\"1.0.0\"` → `\"1.0.1\"`\n198: - `\"1.0.0-alpha.1\"` → `\"1.0.0-alpha.2\"`\n199: - `\"custom-version\"` → `\"custom-version-1\"`\n200: - `None` → `\"0.1.0\"`\n201: \n202: ### BuildRuntime._validate_build_prerequisites()\n203: \n204: ```python\n205: def _validate_build_prerequisites(\n206:     self,\n207:     workspace_path: Path\n208: ) -> None\n209: ```\n210: \n211: **Purpose**: Ensure workspace is ready for build.\n212: \n213: **Parameters**:\n214: - `workspace_path` (Path): Path to workspace\n215: \n216: **Checks**:\n217: 1. Dockerfile exists at `{workspace_path}/Dockerfile`\n218: 2. Docker daemon is available and running\n219: \n220: **Raises**:\n221: - `ValueError`: If Dockerfile not found\n222: - `RuntimeError`: If Docker not available\n223: \n224: ### BuildRuntime._update_build_metadata()\n225: \n226: ```python\n227: def _update_build_metadata(\n228:     self,\n229:     workspace_path: Path,\n230:     metadata: AgentMetadata,\n231:     build_result: Dict[str, str],\n232:     tag: str = \"latest\"\n233: ) -> None\n234: ```\n235: \n236: **Purpose**: Store build results in metadata.\n237: \n238: **Parameters**:\n239: - `workspace_path` (Path): Path to workspace\n240: - `metadata` (AgentMetadata): Agent metadata to update\n241: - `build_result` (Dict[str, str]): Build result from DockerService\n242: - `tag` (str): Image tag (default \"latest\")\n243: \n244: **Behavior**:\n245: - Merges build result into `metadata.image` dictionary\n246: - Saves updated metadata to workspace\n247: \n248: ### DockerService.build_image()\n249: \n250: ```python\n251: def build_image(\n252:     self,\n253:     dockerfile_path: Path,\n254:     context_path: Path,\n255:     image_name: str,\n256:     tag: str = \"latest\",\n257:     build_args: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None\n258: ) -> Dict[str, str]\n259: ```\n260: \n261: **Purpose**: Build Docker image using Docker SDK.\n262: \n263: **Parameters**:\n264: - `dockerfile_path` (Path): Path to Dockerfile\n265: - `context_path` (Path): Build context directory\n266: - `image_name` (str): Base image name\n267: - `tag` (str): Image tag\n268: - `build_args` (Optional[Dict[str, str]]): Docker build arguments\n269: \n270: **Returns**: Dictionary with image_name, image_id, image_size, build_time\n271: \n272: **Behavior**:\n273: - Constructs full image name: `{image_name}:{tag}`\n274: - Calls `docker.from_env().images.build()`\n275: - Retrieves image information using `get_image_info()`\n276: - Adds build timestamp\n277: \n278: ## Error Handling\n279: \n280: ### Error Hierarchy\n281: \n282: ```\n283: Exception\n284: ├── ValueError (User input errors)\n285: │   └── \"Dockerfile not found in workspace\"\n286: │   └── \"No metadata file found in workspace\"\n287: ├── RuntimeError (System errors)\n288: │   └── \"Docker is not available or not running\"\n289: │   └── \"Failed to build Docker image\"\n290: │   └── \"Failed to log in to Docker registry\"\n291: │   └── \"Failed to tag Docker image\"\n292: └── FileNotFoundError\n293:     └── Metadata file not found\n294: ```\n295: \n296: ### Error Handling Strategy\n297: \n298: #### CLI Layer (main.py)\n299: \n300: ```python\n301: def build(...):\n302:     try:\n303:         runtime = BuildRuntime(verbose=verbose)\n304:         result = runtime.build(workspace_path, **options)\n305:         console.print_success(result)\n306:     except Exception as e:\n307:         _handle_error(e, \"building image\", verbose)\n308: ```\n309: \n310: #### Runtime Layer (build_runtime.py)\n311: \n312: ```python\n313: def build(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n314:     original_version = metadata.version\n315:     self._increment_version(workspace_path, metadata)\n316:     \n317:     try:\n318:         result = self._execute_build(...)\n319:         self._update_build_metadata(workspace_path, metadata, result)\n320:         return result\n321:     except Exception as e:\n322:         if original_version != metadata.version:\n323:             self._revert_version(workspace_path, original_version)\n324:         raise\n325: ```\n326: \n327: #### Version Reversion on Failure\n328: \n329: - Store original version before increment\n330: - On build failure, restore original version\n331: - Log warning: \"Build failed, reverting version from X to Y\"\n332: - Save reverted metadata\n333: \n334: #### DockerService Error Handling\n335: \n336: ```python\n337: def check_docker_available(self) -> bool:\n338:     try:\n339:         self.client.ping()\n340:         return True\n341:     except DockerException as e:\n342:         logger.warning(f\"Docker not available: {e}\")\n343:         return False\n344: \n345: def build_image(self, ...):\n346:     if not self.check_docker_available():\n347:         raise RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")\n348:     \n349:     try:\n350:         image, build_logs = self.client.images.build(...)\n351:         return self.get_image_info(full_image_name)\n352:     except DockerException as e:\n353:         raise RuntimeError(f\"Failed to build Docker image: {e}\") from e\n354: ```\n355: \n356: ### User-Facing Error Messages\n357: \n358: | Error | Message | Exit Code |\n359: |-------|---------|-----------|\n360: | Dockerfile not found | \"Dockerfile not found in workspace. Run 'pack' first.\" | 1 |\n361: | Docker unavailable | \"Error building image: Docker is not available or not running\" | 1 |\n362: | Build failure | \"Error building image: Failed to build Docker image: {error}\" | 1 |\n363: | Metadata not found | \"Error building image: No metadata file found in {workspace}\" | 1 |\n364: \n365: ## Testing Strategy\n366: \n367: ### Unit Tests\n368: \n369: #### Test: BuildRuntime._increment_version()\n370: \n371: ```python\n372: def test_increment_semantic_version():\n373:     metadata = AgentMetadata(\n374:         agent_name=\"test\",\n375:         entrypoint=\"python main.py\",\n376:         version=\"1.0.0\"\n377:     )\n378:     runtime = BuildRuntime()\n379:     new_version = runtime._increment_version(Path(\"/tmp\"), metadata)\n380:     assert new_version == \"1.0.1\"\n381:     assert metadata.version == \"1.0.1\"\n382: \n383: def test_increment_prerelease_version():\n384:     metadata = AgentMetadata(\n385:         agent_name=\"test\",\n386:         entrypoint=\"python main.py\",\n387:         version=\"1.0.0-alpha.1\"\n388:     )\n389:     runtime = BuildRuntime()\n390:     new_version = runtime._increment_version(Path(\"/tmp\"), metadata)\n391:     assert new_version == \"1.0.0-alpha.2\"\n392: \n393: def test_increment_custom_version():\n394:     metadata = AgentMetadata(\n395:         agent_name=\"test\",\n396:         entrypoint=\"python main.py\",\n397:         version=\"custom-version\"\n398:     )\n399:     runtime = BuildRuntime()\n400:     new_version = runtime._increment_version(Path(\"/tmp\"), metadata)\n401:     assert new_version == \"custom-version-1\"\n402: \n403: def test_increment_no_version():\n404:     metadata = AgentMetadata(\n405:         agent_name=\"test\",\n406:         entrypoint=\"python main.py\"\n407:     )\n408:     runtime = BuildRuntime()\n409:     new_version = runtime._increment_version(Path(\"/tmp\"), metadata)\n410:     assert new_version == \"0.1.0\"\n411: ```\n412: \n413: #### Test: BuildRuntime._validate_build_prerequisites()\n414: \n415: ```python\n416: def test_validate_missing_dockerfile(tmp_path):\n417:     runtime = BuildRuntime()\n418:     with pytest.raises(ValueError, match=\"Dockerfile not found\"):\n419:         runtime._validate_build_prerequisites(tmp_path)\n420: \n421: def test_validate_docker_unavailable(tmp_path, mocker):\n422:     runtime = BuildRuntime()\n423:     tmp_path.joinpath(\"Dockerfile\").write_text(\"FROM python:3.10\")\n424:     mocker.patch.object(runtime.docker_service, \"check_docker_available\", return_value=False)\n425:     with pytest.raises(RuntimeError, match=\"Docker is not available\"):\n426:         runtime._validate_build_prerequisites(tmp_path)\n427: ```\n428: \n429: #### Test: BuildRuntime.build() - Version Reversion\n430: \n431: ```python\n432: def test_build_reverts_version_on_failure(tmp_path, mocker):\n433:     tmp_path.joinpath(\"agent_metadata.yaml\").write_text(\n434:         \"agent_name: test\\nentrypoint: python main.py\\nversion: 1.0.0\"\n435:     )\n436:     tmp_path.joinpath(\"Dockerfile\").write_text(\"FROM python:3.10\")\n437:     \n438:     runtime = BuildRuntime()\n439:     mocker.patch.object(runtime, \"_build_local\", side_effect=RuntimeError(\"Build failed\"))\n440:     mocker.patch.object(runtime.docker_service, \"check_docker_available\", return_value=True)\n441:     \n442:     with pytest.raises(RuntimeError):\n443:         runtime.build(tmp_path)\n444:     \n445:     metadata = runtime.metadata_service.load_metadata(tmp_path)\n446:     assert metadata.version == \"1.0.0\"  # Reverted\n447: ```\n448: \n449: ### Integration Tests\n450: \n451: #### Test: End-to-End Local Build\n452: \n453: ```python\n454: @pytest.mark.integration\n455: def test_e2e_build_local(tmp_path):\n456:     # Create valid workspace\n457:     tmp_path.joinpath(\"main.py\").write_text(\"print('hello')\")\n458:     tmp_path.joinpath(\"Dockerfile\").write_text(\"FROM python:3.10\\nCOPY main.py .\\nCMD python main.py\")\n459:     tmp_path.joinpath(\"agent_metadata.yaml\").write_text(\n460:         \"agent_name: test-agent\\nentrypoint: python main.py\\nversion: 1.0.0\"\n461:     )\n462:     \n463:     runtime = BuildRuntime()\n464:     result = runtime.build(tmp_path)\n465:     \n466:     assert result[\"image_name\"] == \"test-agent:1.0.1\"\n467:     assert \"image_id\" in result\n468:     assert result[\"image_size\"] != \"0.00 B\"\n469:     \n470:     metadata = runtime.metadata_service.load_metadata(tmp_path)\n471:     assert metadata.version == \"1.0.1\"\n472:     assert metadata.image is not None\n473: ```\n474: \n475: #### Test: Build with Proxy\n476: \n477: ```python\n478: def test_build_with_proxy(tmp_path, mocker):\n479:     tmp_path.joinpath(\"Dockerfile\").write_text(\"FROM python:3.10\")\n480:     tmp_path.joinpath(\"agent_metadata.yaml\").write_text(\n481:         \"agent_name: test\\nentrypoint: python main.py\"\n482:     )\n483:     \n484:     runtime = BuildRuntime()\n485:     build_mock = mocker.patch.object(runtime.docker_service, \"build_image\", return_value={\n486:         \"image_name\": \"test:latest\",\n487:         \"image_id\": \"abc123\",\n488:         \"image_size\": \"100 MB\",\n489:     })\n490:     \n491:     runtime.build(tmp_path, proxy=\"http://proxy.example.com:8080\")\n492:     \n493:     build_mock.assert_called_once()\n494:     call_args = build_mock.call_args\n495:     assert call_args.kwargs[\"build_args\"][\"HTTP_PROXY\"] == \"http://proxy.example.com:8080\"\n496:     assert call_args.kwargs[\"build_args\"][\"HTTPS_PROXY\"] == \"http://proxy.example.com:8080\"\n497: ```\n498: \n499: ### Mocking Strategy\n500: \n501: #### DockerService Mock\n502: \n503: ```python\n504: @pytest.fixture\n505: def mock_docker_service(mocker):\n506:     service = mocker.MagicMock(spec=DockerService)\n507:     service.check_docker_available.return_value = True\n508:     service.build_image.return_value = {\n509:         \"image_name\": \"test:1.0.0\",\n510:         \"image_id\": \"abc123def456\",\n511:         \"image_size\": \"512.34 MB\",\n512:         \"build_time\": 1234567890.0,\n513:     }\n514:     service.get_image_info.return_value = {\n515:         \"image_name\": \"test:1.0.0\",\n516:         \"image_id\": \"abc123def456\",\n517:         \"image_size\": \"512.34 MB\",\n518:         \"size_bytes\": 536870912,\n519:     }\n520:     return service\n521: ```\n522: \n523: #### MetadataService Mock\n524: \n525: ```python\n526: @pytest.fixture\n527: def mock_metadata_service(tmp_path, mocker):\n528:     service = mocker.MagicMock(spec=MetadataService)\n529:     \n530:     def load_side_effect(path):\n531:         return AgentMetadata(\n532:             agent_name=\"test\",\n533:             entrypoint=\"python main.py\",\n534:             version=\"1.0.0\",\n535:             build_mode=\"local\"\n536:         )\n537:     \n538:     service.load_metadata.side_effect = load_side_effect\n539:     service.save_metadata = mocker.MagicMock()\n540:     return service\n541: ```\n542: \n543: ### Test Coverage Goals\n544: \n545: | Component | Target Coverage |\n546: |-----------|-----------------|\n547: | build_runtime.py | 90%+ |\n548: | docker_service.py | 85%+ |\n549: | main.py (build command) | 80%+ |\n550: \n551: ### Test Execution\n552: \n553: ```bash\n554: # Run all tests\n555: pytest tests/\n556: \n557: # Run with coverage\n558: pytest --cov=agentcube.runtime.build_runtime --cov=agentcube.services.docker_service\n559: \n560: # Run integration tests only\n561: pytest -m integration\n562: \n563: # Run unit tests only\n564: pytest -m \"not integration\"\n565: ```\n566: \n567: ## CLI Usage\n568: \n569: ### Basic Usage\n570: \n571: ```bash\n572: # Build from current directory\n573: kubectl-agentcube build\n574: \n575: # Build from specific workspace\n576: kubectl-agentcube build -f /path/to/workspace\n577: \n578: # Build with verbose output\n579: kubectl-agentcube build --verbose\n580: \n581: # Build with proxy\n582: kubectl-agentcube build --proxy http://proxy.example.com:8080\n583: \n584: # Build with cloud provider\n585: kubectl-agentcube build --cloud-provider huawei\n586: ```\n587: \n588: ### Prerequisites\n589: \n590: 1. Workspace must be packed (contains `Dockerfile` and `agent_metadata.yaml`)\n591: 2. Docker daemon must be running (for local builds)\n592: 3. Sufficient disk space for image storage\n593: \n594: ### Output\n595: \n596: ```\n597: ⠋ Building image...\n598: ✓ Successfully built image\n599:   Image name: test-agent:1.0.1\n600:   Image ID: abc123def456\n601:   Image size: 512.34 MB\n602: ```\n603: \n604: ## Dependencies\n605: \n606: ### Required\n607: \n608: - `docker>=6.0.0`: Docker SDK for Python\n609: - `pydantic>=2.0.0`: Data validation (via AgentMetadata)\n610: - `pyyaml>=6.0.0`: YAML parsing (via MetadataService)\n611: \n612: ### Optional\n613: \n614: - `kubernetes>=28.0.0`: Kubernetes support (for cloud builds)\n615: \n616: ## Future Enhancements\n617: \n618: 1. **Multi-platform builds**: Support for `--platform` flag (linux/amd64, linux/arm64)\n619: 2. **Build caching**: Layer caching optimization for faster builds\n620: 3. **Parallel builds**: Support for building multiple workspaces concurrently\n621: 4. **Build hooks**: Pre-build and post-build script execution\n622: 5. **Cloud provider integrations**: Full implementations for AWS, GCP, Azure\n623: 6. **Build metrics**: Detailed build time and size analytics\n624: 7. **Build optimization**: Automatic dependency analysis and layer optimization\n\n(End of file - total 624 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# CLI Build Command Design\n\n**AR**: AR-021 — CLI build 命令  \n**Module**: cmd/cli  \n**Language**: Python  \n**Size**: M\n\n## Overview\n\nThe `build` command is a core component of the AgentCube CLI that builds container images from packaged agent workspaces. It supports both local Docker builds and cloud-based builds, with automatic version management and comprehensive error handling.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Component Diagram\n\n```\n┌─────────────┐\n│   CLI (Typer)   │\n│  main.py     │\n└──────┬──────┘","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cmd/cli/design.md","time":{"start":1775875778402,"end":1775875778425}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875778433,"sessionID":"ses_2858e4900ffeHni7jjmb7lEFcK","part":{"id":"prt_d7a71e744001JuDIsuH0Sg4col","messageID":"msg_d7a71dad6001R2zxk8kpCXJooX","sessionID":"ses_2858e4900ffeHni7jjmb7lEFcK","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-e4bc76ae1a264f8a81a41bf61976b1e2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cmd/cli/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cmd/cli/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Proposal: AR-026 — K8s/AgentCube Provider\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: \n5: 本文档针对 AgentCube CLI 项目中的 Kubernetes 提供商系统进行架构提案。该提案旨在规范和完善两种部署提供商——标准 Kubernetes (k8s) 和 AgentCube CRD (agentcube) 的实现，确保 CLI 工具能够灵活地将 AI 代理部署到不同的 Kubernetes 环境。\n6: \n7: ## 背景\n8: \n9: 当前 AgentCube CLI 项目已经实现了基础的 Kubernetes 部署功能，包括：\n10: \n11: - `KubernetesProvider` 类：使用标准 Kubernetes Deployment 和 NodePort Service 部署\n12: - `AgentCubeProvider` 类：使用 AgentRuntime 自定义资源部署\n13: - CLI 命令集成：publish、invoke、status 支持提供商选择\n14: - Kubernetes Python 客户端集成\n15: \n16: 然而，在代码审查和实际使用中发现了一些需要改进的方面：\n17: \n18: 1. **错误处理不一致**：两个提供商的错误处理逻辑存在差异\n19: 2. **状态监控不完整**：缺乏统一的状态查询和健康检查机制\n20: 3. **配置管理复杂**：两个提供商的配置参数和验证逻辑分散\n21: 4. **扩展性受限**：添加新提供商需要修改核心代码\n22: 5. **测试覆盖不足**：缺乏完整的单元测试和集成测试\n23: \n24: ## 当前实现分析\n25: \n26: ### KubernetesProvider 现状\n27: \n28: ```python\n29: class KubernetesProvider:\n30:     def __init__(\n31:         self,\n32:         namespace: str = \"default\",\n33:         verbose: bool = False,\n34:         kubeconfig: Optional[str] = None,\n35:     ) -> None: ...\n36: \n37:     def deploy_agent(\n38:         self,\n39:         agent_name: str,\n40:         image_url: str,\n41:         port: int,\n42:         entrypoint: Optional[str] = None,\n43:         replicas: int = 1,\n44:         node_port: Optional[int] = None,\n45:         env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n46:     ) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n47: \n48:     def get_agent_status(self, agent_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n49:     def delete_agent(self, agent_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n50: ```\n51: \n52: **功能特性**：\n53: - 创建 Deployment 和 NodePort Service\n54: - 支持副本数配置\n55: - 等待部署就绪（默认 120 秒超时）\n56: - 名称消毒（符合 Kubernetes 命名规范）\n57: - 命名空间自动创建\n58: \n59: ### AgentCubeProvider 现状\n60: \n61: ```python\n62: class AgentCubeProvider:\n63:     def __init__(\n64:         self,\n65:         namespace: str = \"default\",\n66:         verbose: bool = False,\n67:         kubeconfig: Optional[str] = None,\n68:     ) -> None: ...\n69: \n70:     def deploy_agent_runtime(\n71:         self,\n72:         agent_name: str,\n73:         image_url: str,\n74:         port: int,\n75:         entrypoint: Optional[str] = None,\n76:         env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n77:         workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None,\n78:         router_url: Optional[str] = None,\n79:         readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = None,\n80:         readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = None,\n81:     ) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n82: \n83:     def get_agent_runtime(self, name: str, namespace: str) -> Optional[Dict[str, Any]]: ...\n84: ```\n85: \n86: **功能特性**：\n87: - 创建 AgentRuntime 自定义资源\n88: - CRD API: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n89: - 配置工作负载管理器和路由器 URL\n90: - 健康探针配置\n91: - 会话超时设置\n92: \n93: ## 问题陈述\n94: \n95: ### 1. 接口不一致\n96: \n97: 两个提供商的方法签名和返回值存在差异：\n98: \n99: - **方法名称**：`deploy_agent` vs `deploy_agent_runtime`\n100: - **参数名称**：`agent_name` vs `name`（在 `get_agent_runtime` 中）\n101: - **返回值结构**：`KubernetesProvider` 返回详细的部署信息，`AgentCubeProvider` 仅返回基本状态\n102: - **状态查询**：`get_agent_status` vs `get_agent_runtime`\n103: \n104: 这导致：\n105: - 调用方需要针对不同提供商编写不同的代码\n106: - 难以实现统一的错误处理\n107: - 代码维护成本高\n108: \n109: ### 2. 错误处理不完善\n110: \n111: 当前错误处理存在以下问题：\n112: \n113: - **超时处理**：`wait_for_deployment_ready` 超时后直接抛出异常，没有重试机制\n114: - **部分失败**：删除操作忽略 404 错误，但没有日志记录\n115: - **错误信息**：错误消息不够详细，难以调试\n116: - **异常类型**：使用通用的 `ApiException`，缺乏自定义异常\n117: \n118: ### 3. 状态监控缺失\n119: \n120: 当前实现缺乏以下功能：\n121: \n122: - **实时状态更新**：部署后无法实时监控资源状态\n123: - **事件查询**：无法查询 Pod 事件和日志\n124: - **健康检查**：缺乏自定义健康检查机制\n125: - **资源使用监控**：无法监控 CPU、内存使用情况\n126: \n127: ### 4. 配置验证不足\n128: \n129: 两个提供商的配置验证逻辑分散：\n130: \n131: - **参数验证**：某些参数没有进行前置验证\n132: - **依赖检查**：没有检查依赖资源是否存在\n133: - **环境变量**：环境变量读取逻辑重复\n134: - **默认值**：默认值配置不统一\n135: \n136: ### 5. 扩展性受限\n137: \n138: 当前架构存在以下扩展性限制：\n139: \n140: - **硬编码 API**：CRD API 信息硬编码在代码中\n141: - **提供商选择**：添加新提供商需要修改 CLI 代码\n142: - **插件系统**：缺乏插件机制支持自定义提供商\n143: - **配置驱动**：无法通过配置文件自定义提供商行为\n144: \n145: ## 提案方案\n146: \n147: ### 1. 统一提供商接口\n148: \n149: #### 1.1 定义基类接口\n150: \n151: ```python\n152: from abc import ABC, abstractmethod\n153: from typing import Any, Dict, List, Optional\n154: from dataclasses import dataclass\n155: from enum import Enum\n156: \n157: class ProviderStatus(str, Enum):\n158:     \"\"\"提供商状态枚举\"\"\"\n159:     PENDING = \"pending\"\n160:     DEPLOYING = \"deploying\"\n161:     RUNNING = \"running\"\n162:     FAILED = \"failed\"\n163:     NOT_FOUND = \"not_found\"\n164:     ERROR = \"error\"\n165: \n166: @dataclass\n167: class DeploymentResult:\n168:     \"\"\"部署结果数据类\"\"\"\n169:     status: ProviderStatus\n170:     agent_name: str\n171:     namespace: str\n172:     resource_url: Optional[str] = None\n173:     metadata: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None\n174:     error: Optional[str] = None\n175: \n176: @dataclass\n177: class AgentStatus:\n178:     \"\"\"代理状态数据类\"\"\"\n179:     status: ProviderStatus\n180:     agent_name: str\n181:     namespace: str\n182:     replicas: Optional[int] = None\n183:     ready_replicas: Optional[int] = None\n184:     available_replicas: Optional[int] = None\n185:     resource_type: Optional[str] = None\n186:     metadata: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None\n187:     error: Optional[str] = None\n188: \n189: class BaseProvider(ABC):\n190:     \"\"\"提供商基类\"\"\"\n191: \n192:     def __init__(\n193:         self,\n194:         namespace: str = \"default\",\n195:         verbose: bool = False,\n196:         kubeconfig: Optional[str] = None,\n197:         timeout: int = 120,\n198:     ) -> None:\n199:         \"\"\"初始化提供商\n200: \n201:         Args:\n202:             namespace: 命名空间\n203:             verbose: 是否启用详细日志\n204:             kubeconfig: kubeconfig 文件路径\n205:             timeout: 操作超时时间（秒）\n206:         \"\"\"\n207:         self.namespace = namespace\n208:         self.verbose = verbose\n209:         self.kubeconfig = kubeconfig\n210:         self.timeout = timeout\n211: \n212:     @abstractmethod\n213:     def deploy(\n214:         self,\n215:         agent_name: str,\n216:         image_url: str,\n217:         port: int,\n218:         **kwargs: Any,\n219:     ) -> DeploymentResult:\n220:         \"\"\"部署代理\n221: \n222:         Args:\n223:             agent_name: 代理名称\n224:             image_url: 容器镜像 URL\n225:             port: 容器端口\n226:             **kwargs: 其他提供商特定的参数\n227: \n228:         Returns:\n229:             DeploymentResult: 部署结果\n230:         \"\"\"\n231:         pass\n232: \n233:     @abstractmethod\n234:     def get_status(self, agent_name: str) -> AgentStatus:\n235:         \"\"\"获取代理状态\n236: \n237:         Args:\n238:             agent_name: 代理名称\n239: \n240:         Returns:\n241:             AgentStatus: 代理状态\n242:         \"\"\"\n243:         pass\n244: \n245:     @abstractmethod\n246:     def delete(self, agent_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n247:         \"\"\"删除代理\n248: \n249:         Args:\n250:             agent_name: 代理名称\n251: \n252:         Returns:\n253:             Dict[str, Any]: 删除结果\n254:         \"\"\"\n255:         pass\n256: \n257:     @abstractmethod\n258:     def get_provider_type(self) -> str:\n259:         \"\"\"获取提供商类型\n260: \n261:         Returns:\n262:             str: 提供商类型（如 \"k8s\" 或 \"agentcube\"）\n263:         \"\"\"\n264:         pass\n265: \n266:     def validate_config(self, **kwargs: Any) -> List[str]:\n267:         \"\"\"验证配置参数\n268: \n269:         Args:\n270:             **kwargs: 配置参数\n271: \n272:         Returns:\n273:             List[str]: 错误消息列表，空列表表示验证通过\n274:         \"\"\"\n275:         return []\n276: \n277:     def _sanitize_name(self, name: str) -> str:\n278:         \"\"\"消毒名称，符合 Kubernetes 命名规范\n279: \n280:         Args:\n281:             name: 原始名称\n282: \n283:         Returns:\n284:             str: 消毒后的名称\n285:         \"\"\"\n286:         import re\n287:         sanitized = re.sub(r\"[^a-z0-9-]\", \"-\", name.lower())\n288:         sanitized = re.sub(r\"-+\", \"-\", sanitized)\n289:         sanitized = sanitized.strip(\"-\")\n290:         if len(sanitized) > 63:\n291:             sanitized = sanitized[:63].rstrip(\"-\")\n292:         return sanitized or \"agent\"\n293: ```\n294: \n295: #### 1.2 重构 KubernetesProvider\n296: \n297: ```python\n298: class KubernetesProvider(BaseProvider):\n299:     \"\"\"标准 Kubernetes 提供商\"\"\"\n300: \n301:     def __init__(\n302:         self,\n303:         namespace: str = \"default\",\n304:         verbose: bool = False,\n305:         kubeconfig: Optional[str] = None,\n306:         timeout: int = 120,\n307:     ) -> None:\n308:         super().__init__(namespace, verbose, kubeconfig, timeout)\n309:         self._load_kubernetes_config()\n310:         self._core_v1 = client.CoreV1Api()\n311:         self._apps_v1 = client.AppsV1Api()\n312: \n313:     def get_provider_type(self) -> str:\n314:         return \"k8s\"\n315: \n316:     def deploy(\n317:         self,\n318:         agent_name: str,\n319:         image_url: str,\n320:         port: int,\n321:         **kwargs: Any,\n322:     ) -> DeploymentResult:\n323:         \"\"\"部署代理到标准 Kubernetes\"\"\"\n324:         try:\n325:             self._ensure_namespace()\n326: \n327:             sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(agent_name)\n328: \n329:             # 提取参数\n330:             replicas = kwargs.get(\"replicas\", 1)\n331:             node_port = kwargs.get(\"node_port\")\n332:             env_vars = kwargs.get(\"env_vars\")\n333: \n334:             # 验证配置\n335:             config_errors = self.validate_config(replicas=replicas, node_port=node_port)\n336:             if config_errors:\n337:                 return DeploymentResult(\n338:                     status=ProviderStatus.ERROR,\n339:                     agent_name=agent_name,\n340:                     namespace=self.namespace,\n341:                     error=f\"Configuration validation failed: {'; '.join(config_errors)}\",\n342:                 )\n343: \n344:             # 创建 Deployment\n345:             self._create_deployment(\n346:                 sanitized_name, image_url, port, replicas, env_vars\n347:             )\n348: \n349:             # 创建 Service\n350:             service = self._create_service(sanitized_name, port, node_port)\n351: \n352:             # 等待就绪\n353:             self._wait_for_ready(sanitized_name, self.timeout)\n354: \n355:             return DeploymentResult(\n356:                 status=ProviderStatus.RUNNING,\n357:                 agent_name=agent_name,\n358:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n359:                 resource_url=f\"http://localhost:{service.spec.ports[0].node_port}\",\n360:                 metadata={\n361:                     \"deployment_name\": sanitized_name,\n362:                     \"service_name\": sanitized_name,\n363:                     \"replicas\": replicas,\n364:                     \"node_port\": service.spec.ports[0].node_port,\n365:                 },\n366:             )\n367: \n368:         except Exception as e:\n369:             logger.error(f\"Failed to deploy agent {agent_name}: {e}\")\n370:             return DeploymentResult(\n371:                 status=ProviderStatus.FAILED,\n372:                 agent_name=agent_name,\n373:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n374:                 error=str(e),\n375:             )\n376: \n377:     def get_status(self, agent_name: str) -> AgentStatus:\n378:         \"\"\"获取代理状态\"\"\"\n379:         sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(agent_name)\n380: \n381:         try:\n382:             deployment = self._apps_v1.read_namespaced_deployment(\n383:                 sanitized_name, self.namespace\n384:             )\n385: \n386:             return AgentStatus(\n387:                 status=ProviderStatus.RUNNING,\n388:                 agent_name=agent_name,\n389:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n390:                 resource_type=\"Deployment\",\n391:                 replicas=deployment.spec.replicas,\n392:                 ready_replicas=deployment.status.ready_replicas or 0,\n393:                 available_replicas=deployment.status.available_replicas or 0,\n394:             )\n395: \n396:         except ApiException as e:\n397:             if e.status == 404:\n398:                 return AgentStatus(\n399:                     status=ProviderStatus.NOT_FOUND,\n400:                     agent_name=agent_name,\n401:                     namespace=self.namespace,\n402:                 )\n403:             return AgentStatus(\n404:                 status=ProviderStatus.ERROR,\n405:                 agent_name=agent_name,\n406:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n407:                 error=str(e),\n408:             )\n409: \n410:     def delete(self, agent_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n411:         \"\"\"删除代理\"\"\"\n412:         sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(agent_name)\n413: \n414:         results = {}\n415: \n416:         try:\n417:             self._apps_v1.delete_namespaced_deployment(sanitized_name, self.namespace)\n418:             results[\"deployment\"] = \"deleted\"\n419:             logger.info(f\"Deleted deployment {sanitized_name}\")\n420:         except ApiException as e:\n421:             if e.status != 404:\n422:                 logger.warning(f\"Failed to delete deployment: {e}\")\n423:                 results[\"deployment\"] = f\"failed: {e}\"\n424: \n425:         try:\n426:             self._core_v1.delete_namespaced_service(sanitized_name, self.namespace)\n427:             results[\"service\"] = \"deleted\"\n428:             logger.info(f\"Deleted service {sanitized_name}\")\n429:         except ApiException as e:\n430:             if e.status != 404:\n431:                 logger.warning(f\"Failed to delete service: {e}\")\n432:                 results[\"service\"] = f\"failed: {e}\"\n433: \n434:         return {\n435:             \"status\": \"deleted\",\n436:             \"agent_name\": agent_name,\n437:             \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n438:             \"details\": results,\n439:         }\n440: \n441:     def validate_config(self, **kwargs: Any) -> List[str]:\n442:         \"\"\"验证配置参数\"\"\"\n443:         errors = []\n444: \n445:         replicas = kwargs.get(\"replicas\", 1)\n446:         if not isinstance(replicas, int) or replicas < 0:\n447:             errors.append(\"replicas must be a non-negative integer\")\n448: \n449:         node_port = kwargs.get(\"node_port\")\n450:         if node_port is not None:\n451:             if not isinstance(node_port, int) or not (30000 <= node_port <= 32767):\n452:                 errors.append(\"node_port must be between 30000 and 32767\")\n453: \n454:         return errors\n455: \n456:     # ... 其他辅助方法保持不变 ...\n457: ```\n458: \n459: #### 1.3 重构 AgentCubeProvider\n460: \n461: ```python\n462: class AgentCubeProvider(BaseProvider):\n463:     \"\"\"AgentCube AgentRuntime CR 提供商\"\"\"\n464: \n465:     CR_GROUP = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"\n466:     CR_VERSION = \"v1alpha1\"\n467:     CR_PLURAL = \"agentruntimes\"\n468: \n469:     def __init__(\n470:         self,\n471:         namespace: str = \"default\",\n472:         verbose: bool = False,\n473:         kubeconfig: Optional[str] = None,\n474:         timeout: int = 120,\n475:     ) -> None:\n476:         super().__init__(namespace, verbose, kubeconfig, timeout)\n477:         self._load_kubernetes_config()\n478:         self._custom_api = CustomObjectsApi()\n479: \n480:     def get_provider_type(self) -> str:\n481:         return \"agentcube\"\n482: \n483:     def deploy(\n484:         self,\n485:         agent_name: str,\n486:         image_url: str,\n487:         port: int,\n488:         **kwargs: Any,\n489:     ) -> DeploymentResult:\n490:         \"\"\"部署代理使用 AgentRuntime CR\"\"\"\n491:         try:\n492:             self._ensure_namespace()\n493: \n494:             sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(agent_name)\n495: \n496:             # 提取参数\n497:             entrypoint = kwargs.get(\"entrypoint\")\n498:             env_vars = kwargs.get(\"env_vars\")\n499:             workload_manager_url = kwargs.get(\"workload_manager_url\") or os.getenv(\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\")\n500:             router_url = kwargs.get(\"router_url\") or os.getenv(\"ROUTER_URL\")\n501:             readiness_probe_path = kwargs.get(\"readiness_probe_path\", \"/health\")\n502:             readiness_probe_port = kwargs.get(\"readiness_probe_port\", port)\n503: \n504:             # 验证配置\n505:             config_errors = self.validate_config(\n506:                 workload_manager_url=workload_manager_url,\n507:                 router_url=router_url,\n508:             )\n509:             if config_errors:\n510:                 return DeploymentResult(\n511:                     status=ProviderStatus.ERROR,\n512:                     agent_name=agent_name,\n513:                     namespace=self.namespace,\n514:                     error=f\"Configuration validation failed: {'; '.join(config_errors)}\",\n515:                 )\n516: \n517:             # 创建或更新 AgentRuntime CR\n518:             cr = self._build_agent_runtime_cr(\n519:                 sanitized_name, image_url, port, entrypoint, env_vars,\n520:                 workload_manager_url, router_url,\n521:                 readiness_probe_path, readiness_probe_port,\n522:             )\n523: \n524:             self._apply_agent_runtime_cr(sanitized_name, cr)\n525: \n526:             return DeploymentResult(\n527:                 status=ProviderStatus.RUNNING,\n528:                 agent_name=agent_name,\n529:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n530:                 metadata={\n531:                     \"cr_name\": sanitized_name,\n532:                     \"workload_manager_url\": workload_manager_url,\n533:                     \"router_url\": router_url,\n534:                 },\n535:             )\n536: \n537:         except Exception as e:\n538:             logger.error(f\"Failed to deploy agent {agent_name}: {e}\")\n539:             return DeploymentResult(\n540:                 status=ProviderStatus.FAILED,\n541:                 agent_name=agent_name,\n542:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n543:                 error=str(e),\n544:             )\n545: \n546:     def get_status(self, agent_name: str) -> AgentStatus:\n547:         \"\"\"获取代理状态\"\"\"\n548:         sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(agent_name)\n549: \n550:         try:\n551:             cr = self._custom_api.get_namespaced_custom_object(\n552:                 group=self.CR_GROUP,\n553:                 version=self.CR_VERSION,\n554:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n555:                 plural=self.CR_PLURAL,\n556:                 name=sanitized_name,\n557:             )\n558: \n559:             # 从 CR status 中读取状态\n560:             status_data = cr.get(\"status\", {})\n561: \n562:             return AgentStatus(\n563:                 status=ProviderStatus.RUNNING,\n564:                 agent_name=agent_name,\n565:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n566:                 resource_type=\"AgentRuntime\",\n567:                 metadata={\n568:                     \"agent_endpoint\": status_data.get(\"agentEndpoint\"),\n569:                     \"cr_status\": status_data,\n570:                 },\n571:             )\n572: \n573:         except ApiException as e:\n574:             if e.status == 404:\n575:                 return AgentStatus(\n576:                     status=ProviderStatus.NOT_FOUND,\n577:                     agent_name=agent_name,\n578:                     namespace=self.namespace,\n579:                 )\n580:             return AgentStatus(\n581:                 status=ProviderStatus.ERROR,\n582:                 agent_name=agent_name,\n583:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n584:                 error=str(e),\n585:             )\n586: \n587:     def delete(self, agent_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n588:         \"\"\"删除代理\"\"\"\n589:         sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(agent_name)\n590: \n591:         try:\n592:             self._custom_api.delete_namespaced_custom_object(\n593:                 group=self.CR_GROUP,\n594:                 version=self.CR_VERSION,\n595:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n596:                 plural=self.CR_PLURAL,\n597:                 name=sanitized_name,\n598:             )\n599:             logger.info(f\"Deleted AgentRuntime {sanitized_name}\")\n600:             return {\n601:                 \"status\": \"deleted\",\n602:                 \"agent_name\": agent_name,\n603:                 \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n604:                 \"cr_name\": sanitized_name,\n605:             }\n606:         except ApiException as e:\n607:             if e.status == 404:\n608:                 return {\n609:                     \"status\": \"not_found\",\n610:                     \"agent_name\": agent_name,\n611:                     \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n612:                 }\n613:             logger.error(f\"Failed to delete AgentRuntime {sanitized_name}: {e}\")\n614:             return {\n615:                 \"status\": \"failed\",\n616:                 \"agent_name\": agent_name,\n617:                 \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n618:                 \"error\": str(e),\n619:             }\n620: \n621:     def validate_config(self, **kwargs: Any) -> List[str]:\n622:         \"\"\"验证配置参数\"\"\"\n623:         errors = []\n624: \n625:         workload_manager_url = kwargs.get(\"workload_manager_url\") or os.getenv(\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\")\n626:         router_url = kwargs.get(\"router_url\") or os.getenv(\"ROUTER_URL\")\n627: \n628:         if not workload_manager_url:\n629:             errors.append(\"workload_manager_url is required (provide as parameter or WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL env var)\")\n630: \n631:         if not router_url:\n632:             errors.append(\"router_url is required (provide as parameter or ROUTER_URL env var)\")\n633: \n634:         return errors\n635: \n636:     def _build_agent_runtime_cr(\n637:         self,\n638:         name: str,\n639:         image_url: str,\n640:         port: int,\n641:         entrypoint: Optional[str],\n642:         env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]],\n643:         workload_manager_url: str,\n644:         router_url: str,\n645:         readiness_probe_path: str,\n646:         readiness_probe_port: int,\n647:     ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n648:         \"\"\"构建 AgentRuntime CR\"\"\"\n649:         env_list = [\n650:             client.V1EnvVar(name=k, value=v) for k, v in (env_vars or {}).items()\n651:         ]\n652: \n653:         return {\n654:             \"apiVersion\": f\"{self.CR_GROUP}/{self.CR_VERSION}\",\n655:             \"kind\": \"AgentRuntime\",\n656:             \"metadata\": {\n657:                 \"name\": name,\n658:                 \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n659:             },\n660:             \"spec\": {\n661:                 \"image\": image_url,\n662:                 \"port\": port,\n663:                 \"entrypoint\": entrypoint or \"\",\n664:                 \"env\": env_list,\n665:                 \"workloadManagerURL\": workload_manager_url,\n666:                 \"routerURL\": router_url,\n667:                 \"sessionTimeout\": \"15m\",\n668:                 \"maxSessionDuration\": \"8h\",\n669:                 \"readinessProbe\": {\n670:                     \"path\": readiness_probe_path,\n671:                     \"port\": readiness_probe_port,\n672:                 },\n673:                 \"imagePullSecrets\": [{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}],\n674:             },\n675:         }\n676: \n677:     def _apply_agent_runtime_cr(self, name: str, cr: Dict[str, Any]) -> None:\n678:         \"\"\"应用 AgentRuntime CR（创建或更新）\"\"\"\n679:         try:\n680:             self._custom_api.create_namespaced_custom_object(\n681:                 group=self.CR_GROUP,\n682:                 version=self.CR_VERSION,\n683:                 namespace=self.namespace,\n684:                 plural=self.CR_PLURAL,\n685:                 body=cr,\n686:             )\n687:             logger.info(f\"Created AgentRuntime {name}\")\n688:         except ApiException as e:\n689:             if e.status == 409:\n690:                 self._custom_api.replace_namespaced_custom_object(\n691:                     group=self.CR_GROUP,\n692:                     version=self.CR_VERSION,\n693:                     namespace=self.namespace,\n694:                     plural=self.CR_PLURAL,\n695:                     name=name,\n696:                     body=cr,\n697:                 )\n698:                 logger.info(f\"Updated AgentRuntime {name}\")\n699:             else:\n700:                 raise\n701: \n702:     # ... 其他辅助方法保持不变 ...\n703: ```\n704: \n705: ### 2. 提供商工厂\n706: \n707: ```python\n708: from typing import Type\n709: \n710: class ProviderFactory:\n711:     \"\"\"提供商工厂\"\"\"\n712: \n713:     _providers: Dict[str, Type[BaseProvider]] = {}\n714: \n715:     @classmethod\n716:     def register(cls, provider_type: str, provider_class: Type[BaseProvider]) -> None:\n717:         \"\"\"注册提供商\n718: \n719:         Args:\n720:             provider_type: 提供商类型\n721:             provider_class: 提供商类\n722:         \"\"\"\n723:         cls._providers[provider_type] = provider_class\n724:         logger.info(f\"Registered provider: {provider_type}\")\n725: \n726:     @classmethod\n727:     def unregister(cls, provider_type: str) -> None:\n728:         \"\"\"注销提供商\n729: \n730:         Args:\n731:             provider_type: 提供商类型\n732:         \"\"\"\n733:         if provider_type in cls._providers:\n734:             del cls._providers[provider_type]\n735:             logger.info(f\"Unregistered provider: {provider_type}\")\n736: \n737:     @classmethod\n738:     def create(\n739:         cls,\n740:         provider_type: str,\n741:         **kwargs: Any,\n742:     ) -> BaseProvider:\n743:         \"\"\"创建提供商实例\n744: \n745:         Args:\n746:             provider_type: 提供商类型\n747:             **kwargs: 提供商初始化参数\n748: \n749:         Returns:\n750:             BaseProvider: 提供商实例\n751: \n752:         Raises:\n753:             ValueError: 如果提供商类型不存在\n754:         \"\"\"\n755:         if provider_type not in cls._providers:\n756:             raise ValueError(f\"Unknown provider type: {provider_type}. Available: {list(cls._providers.keys())}\")\n757: \n758:         provider_class = cls._providers[provider_type]\n759:         return provider_class(**kwargs)\n760: \n761:     @classmethod\n762:     def list_providers(cls) -> List[str]:\n763:         \"\"\"列出所有已注册的提供商\n764: \n765:         Returns:\n766:             List[str]: 提供商类型列表\n767:         \"\"\"\n768:         return list(cls._providers.keys())\n769: \n770: \n771: # 注册默认提供商\n772: ProviderFactory.register(\"k8s\", KubernetesProvider)\n773: ProviderFactory.register(\"agentcube\", AgentCubeProvider)\n774: ```\n775: \n776: ### 3. 错误处理增强\n777: \n778: #### 3.1 自定义异常\n779: \n780: ```python\n781: class ProviderError(Exception):\n782:     \"\"\"提供商基础异常\"\"\"\n783:     pass\n784: \n785: \n786: class ProviderConfigurationError(ProviderError):\n787:     \"\"\"提供商配置错误\"\"\"\n788:     pass\n789: \n790: \n791: class ProviderDeploymentError(ProviderError):\n792:     \"\"\"提供商部署错误\"\"\"\n793:     pass\n794: \n795: \n796: class ProviderTimeoutError(ProviderError):\n797:     \"\"\"提供商超时错误\"\"\"\n798:     pass\n799: \n800: \n801: class ProviderNotFoundError(ProviderError):\n802:     \"\"\"提供商未找到错误\"\"\"\n803:     pass\n804: ```\n805: \n806: #### 3.2 重试机制\n807: \n808: ```python\n809: import time\n810: from functools import wraps\n811: from typing import Callable, Type\n812: \n813: def retry_on_exception(\n814:     max_attempts: int = 3,\n815:     delay: float = 1.0,\n816:     backoff: float = 2.0,\n817:     exceptions: Tuple[Type[Exception], ...] = (Exception,),\n818: ) -> Callable:\n819:     \"\"\"重试装饰器\n820: \n821:     Args:\n822:         max_attempts: 最大尝试次数\n823:         delay: 初始延迟（秒）\n824:         backoff: 延迟倍增因子\n825:         exceptions: 需要重试的异常类型\n826: \n827:     Returns:\n828:         Callable: 装饰后的函数\n829:     \"\"\"\n830:     def decorator(func: Callable) -> Callable:\n831:         @wraps(func)\n832:         def wrapper(*args: Any, **kwargs: Any) -> Any:\n833:             last_exception = None\n834:             current_delay = delay\n835: \n836:             for attempt in range(max_attempts):\n837:                 try:\n838:                     return func(*args, **kwargs)\n839:                 except exceptions as e:\n840:                     last_exception = e\n841:                     if attempt < max_attempts - 1:\n842:                         logger.warning(\n843:                             f\"Attempt {attempt + 1}/{max_attempts} failed: {e}. \"\n844:                             f\"Retrying in {current_delay}s...\"\n845:                         )\n846:                         time.sleep(current_delay)\n847:                         current_delay *= backoff\n848:                     else:\n849:                         logger.error(f\"All {max_attempts} attempts failed\")\n850: \n851:             raise last_exception  # type: ignore\n852: \n853:         return wrapper\n854:     return decorator\n855: \n856: \n857: # 在 KubernetesProvider 中使用\n858: class KubernetesProvider(BaseProvider):\n859:     @retry_on_exception(\n860:         max_attempts=3,\n861:         delay=2.0,\n862:         exceptions=(ApiException,),\n863:     )\n864:     def _wait_for_ready(self, name: str, timeout: int) -> None:\n865:         \"\"\"等待部署就绪（带重试）\"\"\"\n866:         start_time = time.time()\n867: \n868:         while time.time() - start_time < timeout:\n869:             try:\n870:                 deployment = self._apps_v1.read_namespaced_deployment(name, self.namespace)\n871:                 if (\n872:                     deployment.status.ready_replicas is not None\n873:                     and deployment.status.ready_replicas >= deployment.spec.replicas\n874:                 ):\n875:                     logger.info(f\"Deployment {name} is ready\")\n876:                     return\n877:             except ApiException as e:\n878:                 logger.warning(f\"Error checking deployment status: {e}\")\n879: \n880:             time.sleep(2)\n881: \n882:         raise ProviderTimeoutError(\n883:             f\"Deployment {name} did not become ready within {timeout} seconds\"\n884:         )\n885: ```\n886: \n887: ### 4. 状态监控增强\n888: \n889: ```python\n890: from typing import List, Dict, Any, Optional\n891: from datetime import datetime, timedelta\n892: \n893: class StatusMonitor:\n894:     \"\"\"状态监控器\"\"\"\n895: \n896:     def __init__(\n897:         self,\n898:         provider: BaseProvider,\n899:         agent_name: str,\n900:         poll_interval: int = 5,\n901:     ) -> None:\n902:         \"\"\"初始化状态监控器\n903: \n904:         Args:\n905:             provider: 提供商实例\n906:             agent_name: 代理名称\n907:             poll_interval: 轮询间隔（秒）\n908:         \"\"\"\n909:         self.provider = provider\n910:         self.agent_name = agent_name\n911:         self.poll_interval = poll_interval\n912:         self._monitoring = False\n913: \n914:     def monitor(\n915:         self,\n916:         duration: Optional[int] = None,\n917:         callback: Optional[Callable[[AgentStatus], None]] = None,\n918:     ) -> List[AgentStatus]:\n919:         \"\"\"监控代理状态\n920: \n921:         Args:\n922:             duration: 监控持续时间（秒），None 表示无限\n923:             callback: 状态回调函数\n924: \n925:         Returns:\n926:             List[AgentStatus]: 状态历史\n927:         \"\"\"\n928:         self._monitoring = True\n929:         status_history: List[AgentStatus] = []\n930: \n931:         start_time = datetime.now()\n932: \n933:         while self._monitoring:\n934:             try:\n935:                 status = self.provider.get_status(self.agent_name)\n936:                 status_history.append(status)\n937: \n938:                 if callback:\n939:                     callback(status)\n940: \n941:                 # 检查是否应该停止\n942:                 if status.status in [ProviderStatus.FAILED, ProviderStatus.ERROR]:\n943:                     logger.error(f\"Agent {self.agent_name} failed or errored\")\n944:                     break\n945: \n946:                 if duration and (datetime.now() - start_time).total_seconds() >= duration:\n947:                     break\n948: \n949:             except Exception as e:\n950:                 logger.error(f\"Error monitoring agent {self.agent_name}: {e}\")\n951: \n952:             time.sleep(self.poll_interval)\n953: \n954:         self._monitoring = False\n955:         return status_history\n956: \n957:     def stop(self) -> None:\n958:         \"\"\"停止监控\"\"\"\n959:         self._monitoring = False\n960: \n961:     def wait_for_status(\n962:         self,\n963:         target_status: ProviderStatus,\n964:         timeout: int = 120,\n965:     ) -> AgentStatus:\n966:         \"\"\"等待代理达到目标状态\n967: \n968:         Args:\n969:             target_status: 目标状态\n970:             timeout: 超时时间（秒）\n971: \n972:         Returns:\n973:             AgentStatus: 最终状态\n974: \n975:         Raises:\n976:             ProviderTimeoutError: 超时\n977:         \"\"\"\n978:         start_time = datetime.now()\n979: \n980:         while (datetime.now() - start_time).total_seconds() < timeout:\n981:             status = self.provider.get_status(self.agent_name)\n982: \n983:             if status.status == target_status:\n984:                 return status\n985: \n986:             if status.status in [ProviderStatus.FAILED, ProviderStatus.ERROR]:\n987:                 raise ProviderError(\n988:                     f\"Agent {self.agent_name} failed or errored: {status.error}\"\n989:                 )\n990: \n991:             time.sleep(self.poll_interval)\n992: \n993:         raise ProviderTimeoutError(\n994:             f\"Agent {self.agent_name} did not reach status {target_status} within {timeout} seconds\"\n995:         )\n996: \n997: \n998: class EventMonitor:\n999:     \"\"\"事件监控器\"\"\"\n1000: \n1001:     def __init__(\n1002:         self,\n1003:         provider: BaseProvider,\n1004:         agent_name: str,\n1005:     ) -> None:\n1006:         \"\"\"初始化事件监控器\n1007: \n1008:         Args:\n1009:             provider: 提供商实例\n1010:             agent_name: 代理名称\n1011:         \"\"\"\n1012:         self.provider = provider\n1013:         self.agent_name = agent_name\n1014: \n1015:         if isinstance(provider, KubernetesProvider):\n1016:             self._core_v1 = client.CoreV1Api()\n1017: \n1018:     def get_events(\n1019:         self,\n1020:         since: Optional[datetime] = None,\n1021:     ) -> List[Dict[str, Any]]:\n1022:         \"\"\"获取代理相关事件\n1023: \n1024:         Args:\n1025:             since: 起始时间\n1026: \n1027:         Returns:\n1028:             List[Dict[str, Any]]: 事件列表\n1029:         \"\"\"\n1030:         if not isinstance(self.provider, KubernetesProvider):\n1031:             return []\n1032: \n1033:         sanitized_name = self.provider._sanitize_name(self.agent_name)\n1034: \n1035:         try:\n1036:             events = self._core_v1.list_namespaced_event(\n1037:                 self.provider.namespace,\n1038:                 field_selector=f\"involvedObject.name={sanitized_name}\",\n1039:             )\n1040: \n1041:             event_list = []\n1042:             for event in events.items:\n1043:                 if since and event.last_timestamp < since:\n1044:                     continue\n1045: \n1046:                 event_list.append({\n1047:                     \"type\": event.type,\n1048:                     \"reason\": event.reason,\n1049:                     \"message\": event.message,\n1050:                     \"timestamp\": event.last_timestamp,\n1051:                 })\n1052: \n1053:             return event_list\n1054: \n1055:         except Exception as e:\n1056:             logger.error(f\"Failed to get events: {e}\")\n1057:             return []\n1058: \n1059:     def get_pod_logs(\n1060:         self,\n1061:         container_name: Optional[str] = None,\n1062:         tail_lines: int = 100,\n1063:     ) -> List[str]:\n1064:         \"\"\"获取 Pod 日志\n1065: \n1066:         Args:\n1067:             container_name: 容器名称\n1068:             tail_lines: 日志行数\n1069: \n1070:         Returns:\n1071:             List[str]: 日志行\n1072:         \"\"\"\n1073:         if not isinstance(self.provider, KubernetesProvider):\n1074:             return []\n1075: \n1076:         sanitized_name = self.provider._sanitize_name(self.agent_name)\n1077: \n1078:         try:\n1079:             # 获取 Pod 列表\n1080:             pods = self._core_v1.list_namespaced_pod(\n1081:                 self.provider.namespace,\n1082:                 label_selector=f\"app={sanitized_name}\",\n1083:             )\n1084: \n1085:             logs = []\n1086:             for pod in pods.items:\n1087:                 try:\n1088:                     pod_logs = self._core_v1.read_namespaced_pod_log(\n1089:                         pod.metadata.name,\n1090:                         self.provider.namespace,\n1091:                         container=container_name,\n1092:                         tail_lines=tail_lines,\n1093:                     )\n1094:                     logs.append(f\"=== Pod: {pod.metadata.name} ===\")\n1095:                     logs.extend(pod_logs.split(\"\\n\"))\n1096:                 except Exception as e:\n1097:                     logger.warning(f\"Failed to get logs for pod {pod.metadata.name}: {e}\")\n1098: \n1099:             return logs\n1100: \n1101:         except Exception as e:\n1102:             logger.error(f\"Failed to get pod logs: {e}\")\n1103:             return []\n1104: ```\n1105: \n1106: ### 5. 配置管理优化\n1107: \n1108: #### 5.1 配置验证器\n1109: \n1110: ```python\n1111: class ConfigValidator:\n1112:     \"\"\"配置验证器\"\"\"\n1113: \n1114:     @staticmethod\n1115:     def validate_provider_config(\n1116:         provider_type: str,\n1117:         **kwargs: Any,\n1118:     ) -> List[str]:\n1119:         \"\"\"验证提供商配置\n1120: \n1121:         Args:\n1122:             provider_type: 提供商类型\n1123:             **kwargs: 配置参数\n1124: \n1125:         Returns:\n1126:             List[str]: 错误消息列表\n1127:         \"\"\"\n1128:         try:\n1129:             provider = ProviderFactory.create(provider_type, verbose=False)\n1130:             return provider.validate_config(**kwargs)\n1131:         except Exception as e:\n1132:             return [f\"Failed to validate config: {e}\"]\n1133: \n1134:     @staticmethod\n1135:     def validate_k8s_config(\n1136:         replicas: Optional[int] = None,\n1137:         node_port: Optional[int] = None,\n1138:     ) -> List[str]:\n1139:         \"\"\"验证 Kubernetes 配置\n1140: \n1141:         Args:\n1142:             replicas: 副本数\n1143:             node_port: NodePort\n1144: \n1145:         Returns:\n1146:             List[str]: 错误消息列表\n1147:         \"\"\"\n1148:         errors = []\n1149: \n1150:         if replicas is not None:\n1151:             if not isinstance(replicas, int) or replicas < 0:\n1152:                 errors.append(\"replicas must be a non-negative integer\")\n1153: \n1154:         if node_port is not None:\n1155:             if not isinstance(node_port, int) or not (30000 <= node_port <= 32767):\n1156:                 errors.append(\"node_port must be between 30000 and 32767\")\n1157: \n1158:         return errors\n1159: \n1160:     @staticmethod\n1161:     def validate_agentcube_config(\n1162:         workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None,\n1163:         router_url: Optional[str] = None,\n1164:     ) -> List[str]:\n1165:         \"\"\"验证 AgentCube 配置\n1166: \n1167:         Args:\n1168:             workload_manager_url: 工作负载管理器 URL\n1169:             router_url: 路由器 URL\n1170: \n1171:         Returns:\n1172:             List[str]: 错误消息列表\n1173:         \"\"\"\n1174:         errors = []\n1175: \n1176:         workload_manager = workload_manager_url or os.getenv(\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\")\n1177:         router = router_url or os.getenv(\"ROUTER_URL\")\n1178: \n1179:         if not workload_manager:\n1180:             errors.append(\"workload_manager_url is required\")\n1181: \n1182:         if not router:\n1183:             errors.append(\"router_url is required\")\n1184: \n1185:         return errors\n1186: ```\n1187: \n1188: #### 5.2 配置管理器\n1189: \n1190: ```python\n1191: from pathlib import Path\n1192: from typing import Dict, Any, Optional\n1193: \n1194: class ProviderConfigManager:\n1195:     \"\"\"提供商配置管理器\"\"\"\n1196: \n1197:     DEFAULT_CONFIG_FILE = Path.home() / \".agentcube\" / \"providers.yaml\"\n1198: \n1199:     def __init__(self, config_file: Optional[Path] = None) -> None:\n1200:         \"\"\"初始化配置管理器\n1201: \n1202:         Args:\n1203:             config_file: 配置文件路径\n1204:         \"\"\"\n1205:         self.config_file = config_file or self.DEFAULT_CONFIG_FILE\n1206:         self.configs: Dict[str, Any] = self._load_configs()\n1207: \n1208:     def _load_configs(self) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n1209:         \"\"\"加载配置\"\"\"\n1210:         if self.config_file.exists():\n1211:             import yaml\n1212:             with open(self.config_file, \"r\") as f:\n1213:                 return yaml.safe_load(f) or {}\n1214:         return {}\n1215: \n1216:     def _save_configs(self) -> None:\n1217:         \"\"\"保存配置\"\"\"\n1218:         import yaml\n1219:         self.config_file.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n1220:         with open(self.config_file, \"w\") as f:\n1221:             yaml.dump(self.configs, f, default_flow_style=False, indent=2)\n1222: \n1223:     def get_config(\n1224:         self,\n1225:         provider_type: str,\n1226:         key: Optional[str] = None,\n1227:         default: Any = None,\n1228:     ) -> Any:\n1229:         \"\"\"获取配置\n1230: \n1231:         Args:\n1232:             provider_type: 提供商类型\n1233:             key: 配置键\n1234:             default: 默认值\n1235: \n1236:         Returns:\n1237:             Any: 配置值\n1238:         \"\"\"\n1239:         provider_config = self.configs.get(provider_type, {})\n1240: \n1241:         if key:\n1242:             return provider_config.get(key, default)\n1243: \n1244:         return provider_config\n1245: \n1246:     def set_config(\n1247:         self,\n1248:         provider_type: str,\n1249:         key: str,\n1250:         value: Any,\n1251:     ) -> None:\n1252:         \"\"\"设置配置\n1253: \n1254:         Args:\n1255:             provider_type: 提供商类型\n1256:             key: 配置键\n1257:             value: 配置值\n1258:         \"\"\"\n1259:         if provider_type not in self.configs:\n1260:             self.configs[provider_type] = {}\n1261: \n1262:         self.configs[provider_type][key] = value\n1263:         self._save_configs()\n1264: \n1265:     def get_provider_kwargs(\n1266:         self,\n1267:         provider_type: str,\n1268:     ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n1269:         \"\"\"获取提供商初始化参数\n1270: \n1271:         Args:\n1272:             provider_type: 提供商类型\n1273: \n1274:         Returns:\n1275:             Dict[str, Any]: 参数字典\n1276:         \"\"\"\n1277:         provider_config = self.configs.get(provider_type, {})\n1278: \n1279:         kwargs = {}\n1280:         if \"namespace\" in provider_config:\n1281:             kwargs[\"namespace\"] = provider_config[\"namespace\"]\n1282:         if \"kubeconfig\" in provider_config:\n1283:             kwargs[\"kubeconfig\"] = provider_config[\"kubeconfig\"]\n1284:         if \"timeout\" in provider_config:\n1285:             kwargs[\"timeout\"] = provider_config[\"timeout\"]\n1286: \n1287:         return kwargs\n1288: ```\n1289: \n1290: ### 6. 扩展性增强\n1291: \n1292: #### 6.1 插件系统\n1293: \n1294: ```python\n1295: class ProviderPlugin(ABC):\n1296:     \"\"\"提供商插件基类\"\"\"\n1297: \n1298:     @property\n1299:     @abstractmethod\n1300:     def name(self) -> str:\n1301:         \"\"\"插件名称\"\"\"\n1302:         pass\n1303: \n1304:     @property\n1305:     @abstractmethod\n1306:     def provider_type(self) -> str:\n1307:         \"\"\"提供商类型\"\"\"\n1308:         pass\n1309: \n1310:     @abstractmethod\n1311:     def create_provider(\n1312:         self,\n1313:         **kwargs: Any,\n1314:     ) -> BaseProvider:\n1315:         \"\"\"创建提供商实例\n1316: \n1317:         Args:\n1318:             **kwargs: 提供商初始化参数\n1319: \n1320:         Returns:\n1321:             BaseProvider: 提供商实例\n1322:         \"\"\"\n1323:         pass\n1324: \n1325:     @abstractmethod\n1326:     def validate_config(self, **kwargs: Any) -> List[str]:\n1327:         \"\"\"验证配置\n1328: \n1329:         Args:\n1330:             **kwargs: 配置参数\n1331: \n1332:         Returns:\n1333:             List[str]: 错误消息列表\n1334:         \"\"\"\n1335:         pass\n1336: \n1337: \n1338: class ProviderPluginManager:\n1339:     \"\"\"提供商插件管理器\"\"\"\n1340: \n1341:     def __init__(self) -> None:\n1342:         self.plugins: Dict[str, ProviderPlugin] = {}\n1343: \n1344:     def register_plugin(self, plugin: ProviderPlugin) -> None:\n1345:         \"\"\"注册插件\n1346: \n1347:         Args:\n1348:             plugin: 插件实例\n1349:         \"\"\"\n1350:         self.plugins[plugin.name] = plugin\n1351: \n1352:         # 自动注册提供商\n1353:         ProviderFactory.register(\n1354:             plugin.provider_type,\n1355:             plugin.create_provider.__class__,\n1356:         )\n1357: \n1358:         logger.info(f\"Registered provider plugin: {plugin.name}\")\n1359: \n1360:     def unregister_plugin(self, plugin_name: str) -> None:\n1361:         \"\"\"注销插件\n1362: \n1363:         Args:\n1364:             plugin_name: 插件名称\n1365:         \"\"\"\n1366:         if plugin_name in self.plugins:\n1367:             plugin = self.plugins[plugin_name]\n1368:             ProviderFactory.unregister(plugin.provider_type)\n1369:             del self.plugins[plugin_name]\n1370:             logger.info(f\"Unregistered provider plugin: {plugin_name}\")\n1371: \n1372:     def get_plugin(self, plugin_name: str) -> Optional[ProviderPlugin]:\n1373:         \"\"\"获取插件\n1374: \n1375:         Args:\n1376:             plugin_name: 插件名称\n1377: \n1378:         Returns:\n1379:             Optional[ProviderPlugin]: 插件实例\n1380:         \"\"\"\n1381:         return self.plugins.get(plugin_name)\n1382: \n1383:     def list_plugins(self) -> List[str]:\n1384:         \"\"\"列出所有插件\n1385: \n1386:         Returns:\n1387:             List[str]: 插件名称列表\n1388:         \"\"\"\n1389:         return list(self.plugins.keys())\n1390: \n1391: \n1392: # 全局插件管理器实例\n1393: plugin_manager = ProviderPluginManager()\n1394: ```\n1395: \n1396: ## 实施计划\n1397: \n1398: ### 阶段一：接口重构（1周）\n1399: \n1400: **目标**：统一提供商接口和返回值\n1401: \n1402: **任务**：\n1403: 1. 实现 `BaseProvider` 基类和相关数据类\n1404: 2. 重构 `KubernetesProvider` 实现新接口\n1405: 3. 重构 `AgentCubeProvider` 实现新接口\n1406: 4. 添加单元测试覆盖新接口\n1407: \n1408: **交付物**：\n1409: - 统一的提供商接口代码\n1410: - 重构后的两个提供商类\n1411: - 单元测试覆盖率 > 80%\n1412: \n1413: ### 阶段二：工厂和配置（1周）\n1414: \n1415: **目标**：实现提供商工厂和配置管理\n1416: \n1417: **任务**：\n1418: 1. 实现 `ProviderFactory` 工厂类\n1419: 2. 实现 `ConfigValidator` 验证器\n1420: 3. 实现 `ProviderConfigManager` 配置管理器\n1421: 4. 编写配置管理文档\n1422: \n1423: **交付物**：\n1424: - 提供商工厂代码\n1425: - 配置验证和管理代码\n1426: - 配置管理文档\n1427: \n1428: ### 阶段三：错误处理和重试（1周）\n1429: \n1430: **目标**：完善错误处理和重试机制\n1431: \n1432: **任务**：\n1433: 1. 实现自定义异常类\n1434: 2. 实现重试装饰器\n1435: 3. 更新提供商类使用新异常和重试\n1436: 4. 添加错误处理测试\n1437: \n1438: **交付物**：\n1439: - 自定义异常类代码\n1440: - 重试机制代码\n1441: - 更新的提供商类\n1442: - 错误处理测试\n1443: \n1444: ### 阶段四：状态监控（1周）\n1445: \n1446: **目标**：实现状态监控和事件查询\n1447: \n1448: **任务**：\n1449: 1. 实现 `StatusMonitor` 监控器\n1450: 2. 实现 `EventMonitor` 事件监控器\n1451: 3. 添加日志查询功能\n1452: 4. 编写监控使用示例\n1453: \n1454: **交付物**：\n1455: - 状态监控代码\n1456: - 事件监控代码\n1457: - 使用示例和文档\n1458: \n1459: ### 阶段五：插件系统（1周）\n1460: \n1461: **目标**：实现插件系统支持扩展\n1462: \n1463: **任务**：\n1464: 1. 实现 `ProviderPlugin` 基类\n1465: 2. 实现 `ProviderPluginManager` 管理器\n1466: 3. 编写插件开发文档\n1467: 4. 实现示例插件\n1468: \n1469: **交付物**：\n1470: - 插件系统代码\n1471: - 示例插件\n1472: - 插件开发文档\n1473: \n1474: ### 阶段六：集成和测试（1周）\n1475: \n1476: **目标**：全面集成并进行测试\n1477: \n1478: **任务**：\n1479: 1. 更新 CLI 命令使用新接口\n1480: 2. 编写集成测试\n1481: 3. 进行端到端测试\n1482: 4. 性能测试和优化\n1483: \n1484: **交付物**：\n1485: - 更新的 CLI 命令\n1486: - 集成测试套件\n1487: - 端到端测试报告\n1488: - 性能测试报告\n1489: \n1490: ### 阶段七：文档和发布（1周）\n1491: \n1492: **目标**：完善文档并准备发布\n1493: \n1494: **任务**：\n1495: 1. 更新 API 文档\n1496: 2. 编写用户指南\n1497: 3. 编写迁移指南\n1498: 4. 准备版本发布\n1499: \n1500: **交付物**：\n1501: - 完整的 API 文档\n1502: - 用户指南\n1503: - 迁移指南\n1504: - 版本发布说明\n1505: \n1506: ## 影响分析\n1507: \n1508: ### 向后兼容性\n1509: \n1510: **兼容性保证**：\n1511: - 保留原有的 `deploy_agent` 和 `deploy_agent_runtime` 方法（作为废弃 API）\n1512: - 保留原有的参数名称\n1513: - 保留原有的返回值字段\n1514: - 提供适配层兼容旧代码\n1515: \n1516: **迁移策略**：\n1517: 1. 标记旧方法为 `@deprecated`\n1518: 2. 提供迁移脚本转换旧代码\n1519: 3. 在文档中明确说明迁移步骤\n1520: 4. 保留旧 API 两个版本周期\n1521: \n1522: ### 性能影响\n1523: \n1524: **预期影响**：\n1525: - 接口重构：无明显性能影响\n1526: - 重试机制：失败场景下增加延迟\n1527: - 状态监控：定期轮询增加网络开销\n1528: - 配置缓存：减少配置读取时间\n1529: \n1530: **优化措施**：\n1531: - 使用连接池减少连接开销\n1532: - 异步状态查询\n1533: - 缓存配置和状态信息\n1534: - 限制监控频率\n1535: \n1536: ### 依赖变更\n1537: \n1538: **新增依赖**：\n1539: - 无新增外部依赖（使用现有 Kubernetes 客户端）\n1540: \n1541: **版本要求**：\n1542: - `kubernetes>=28.0.0`（保持不变）\n1543: - `typer[all]>=0.9.0`（保持不变）\n1544: - `pydantic>=2.0.0`（保持不变）\n1545: \n1546: ## 风险评估\n1547: \n1548: ### 高风险\n1549: \n1550: 1. **接口变更兼容性**\n1551:    - 风险：现有代码依赖旧接口\n1552:    - 缓解：提供适配层，详细文档，保持旧 API 可用\n1553: \n1554: 2. **状态监控性能**\n1555:    - 风险：频繁轮询影响集群性能\n1556:    - 缓解：限制轮询频率，支持事件驱动模式\n1557: \n1558: ### 中风险\n1559: \n1560: 1. **配置迁移**\n1561:    - 风险：用户配置文件需要迁移\n1562:    - 缓解：提供自动迁移工具，保留旧配置支持\n1563: \n1564: 2. **插件生态**\n1565:    - 风险：缺乏插件导致扩展能力未充分利用\n1566:    - 缓解：提供核心插件集合和开发指南\n1567: \n1568: ### 低风险\n1569: \n1570: 1. **测试覆盖**\n1571:    - 风险：新增功能测试覆盖不足\n1572:    - 缓解：制定测试计划，使用 TDD 方法\n1573: \n1574: 2. **文档完整性**\n1575:    - 风险：文档更新滞后\n1576:    - 缓解：文档与代码同步更新，自动化文档生成\n1577: \n1578: ## 成功指标\n1579: \n1580: ### 技术指标\n1581: \n1582: - 单元测试覆盖率 > 85%\n1583: - 集成测试覆盖率 > 70%\n1584: - 部署成功率 > 95%\n1585: - 状态查询响应时间 < 1s\n1586: - 重试成功率 > 80%\n1587: \n1588: ### 质量指标\n1589: \n1590: - 代码审查通过率 100%\n1591: - 静态分析无严重问题\n1592: - 文档完整性 > 90%\n1593: - API 一致性评分 > 9/10\n1594: \n1595: ### 用户体验指标\n1596: \n1597: - 部署错误率降低 50%\n1598: - 配置错误捕获率 > 90%\n1599: - 用户满意度调查 > 8/10\n1600: - 文档可读性评分 > 8/10\n1601: \n1602: ## 备选方案\n1603: \n1604: ### 方案 A：最小化改动\n1605: \n1606: **描述**：仅统一方法签名，保持其他实现不变\n1607: \n1608: **优点**：\n1609: - 改动范围小\n1610: - 风险低\n1611: - 实施快速\n1612: \n1613: **缺点**：\n1614: - 不解决错误处理问题\n1615: - 状态监控仍然缺失\n1616: - 扩展性未改善\n1617: \n1618: ### 方案 B：完全重构\n1619: \n1620: **描述**：完全重写提供商系统，采用新架构\n1621: \n1622: **优点**：\n1623: - 彻底解决现有问题\n1624: - 更好的架构设计\n1625: - 长期维护成本低\n1626: \n1627: **缺点**：\n1628: - 实施周期长\n1629: - 兼容性挑战大\n1630: - 风险高\n1631: \n1632: ### 推荐方案：渐进式增强\n1633: \n1634: 采用本提案的方案，通过分阶段实施，在保证兼容性的同时逐步增强功能。\n1635: \n1636: ## 结论\n1637: \n1638: 本提案通过统一提供商接口、完善错误处理、增强状态监控、优化配置管理和扩展插件系统，显著改善了 K8s/AgentCube Provider 的架构。该方案在保持向后兼容性的同时，提供了更好的扩展性、可维护性和用户体验。\n1639: \n1640: 建议按照实施计划分阶段推进，每个阶段都有明确的交付物和验证标准，确保项目质量和进度可控。\n\n(End of file - total 1640 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Proposal: AR-026 — K8s/AgentCube Provider\n\n## 概述\n\n本文档针对 AgentCube CLI 项目中的 Kubernetes 提供商系统进行架构提案。该提案旨在规范和完善两种部署提供商——标准 Kubernetes (k8s) 和 AgentCube CRD (agentcube) 的实现，确保 CLI 工具能够灵活地将 AI 代理部署到不同的 Kubernetes 环境。\n\n## 背景\n\n当前 AgentCube CLI 项目已经实现了基础的 Kubernetes 部署功能，包括：\n\n- `KubernetesProvider` 类：使用标准 Kubernetes Deployment 和 NodePort Service 部署\n- `AgentCubeProvider` 类：使用 AgentRuntime 自定义资源部署\n- CLI 命令集成：publish、invoke、status 支持提供商选择\n- Kubernetes Python 客户端集成\n\n然而，在代码审查和实际使用中发现了一些需要改进的方面：\n\n1. **错误处理不一致**：两个提供商的错误处理逻辑存在差异\n2. **状态监控不完整**：缺乏统一的状态查询和健康检查机制\n3. **配置管理复杂**：两个提供商的配置参数和验证逻辑分散","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cmd/cli/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775875778404,"end":1775875778428}}}}
